description: The Tarrant County Public Health (TCPH) and Biosense collaboration is an effort to visualize TCPH health data collected by Biosense using Google Fusion Table technology and make that visualization publicly available. The data consists of patient visits to hospital emergency departments associated with Tarrant County Public Health (TCPH) that had the illness Gastro Intestinal, Heat Related, or Upper Respiratory divided by all emergency department visits that occurred for the same time period and in the geographic granularity for which the calculation was made.

publisher.name: Centers for Disease Control and Prevention, Department of Health & Human Services

title: CDC BioSense: Tarrant County, Texas
